{
  "stem": "11184.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is when, you know, I was saved.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Auschwitz, at least you had a choice-- a chance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a chance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So here I am-- and my mother too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To look.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was-- this was two weeks before--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--when the others left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The others--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did not go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my intuition told me, you are not going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, just was one box, one box train, you know, with who knows how many people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We couldn't-- we had to stand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't even sit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And with the buckets-- the buckets of-- of all the waste right there, coming in, out, and out, and in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was-- I mean, we still didn't know where we going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We still--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't stay long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took off, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It took off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, I wouldn't know that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no-- not days-- no, no, no-- hours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, hours.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and when I arrived there, and I looked out through a hole, it was a funny way how I felt.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said to my mother, this is not for us-- when we arrived at Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I looked out, and I saw people, you know-- dark black.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I thought they're gypsies, because they sent in gypsies to the ghetto one time-- at one time-- not with us, but adjacent to us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They send them in, and-- and then they said that they took them out to kill.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is-- that-- those were the rumors at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I said, oh.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "These are the gypsies here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's not for us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We're not going out here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Look at that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This is not a place for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
